      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Walks PubMed Central Open Access via OAI-PMH protocol  \u00b7  Parses JATS XML by section (abstract / methods / results / discussion)\nEmbeds chunks with text-embedding-3-large @ 1536  \u00b7  Writes to BOTH stores  (Supabase guideline_chunks table + Qdrant qwiva_docs)\nSame embedding model as CPG and pdf-pipeline \u2192 all three pipelines share one vector space",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
