    {
      "id": "supabase_b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1128,
      "width": 1120,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0c4a6e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 77100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745900000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Three chunk tables (one per corpus)\n  \u00b7 clinical_practice_guideline_chunks  \u2190 CPG  +  pdf-pipeline  write here\n  \u00b7 guideline_chunks                     \u2190 PMC writes here  (PubMed)\n  \u00b7 drug_label_chunks                    \u2190 FDA SPL + EMC drug labels\n\nPer row:  id (UUID5)  \u00b7  content  \u00b7  contextual_text  \u00b7  embedding vector(1536)\n          fts tsvector (GIN index)  \u00b7  guideline_title \u00b7 publisher \u00b7 year \u00b7 chunk_type \u00b7 grade \u00b7 ...\n\nRAG path used:  Full-text search via search_cpg_fts / search_pubmed_fts RPCs",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Three chunk tables (one per corpus)\n  \u00b7 clinical_practice_guideline_chunks  \u2190 CPG  +  pdf-pipeline  write here\n  \u00b7 guideline_chunks                     \u2190 PMC writes here  (PubMed)\n  \u00b7 drug_label_chunks                    \u2190 FDA SPL + EMC drug labels\n\nPer row:  id (UUID5)  \u00b7  content  \u00b7  contextual_text  \u00b7  embedding vector(1536)\n          fts tsvector (GIN index)  \u00b7  guideline_title \u00b7 publisher \u00b7 year \u00b7 chunk_type \u00b7 grade \u00b7 ...\n\nRAG path used:  Full-text search via search_cpg_fts / search_pubmed_fts RPCs",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
