      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 54833,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745900000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Single collection:  qwiva_docs\n  \u00b7 1536-dim vectors  \u00b7  Cosine distance  \u00b7  HNSW index  \u00b7  INT8 quantization\n\nFilled by:  CPG pipeline (auto)   \u00b7   PMC pipeline (auto)   \u00b7   pdf-pipeline (NOT auto)\nSame chunk id (UUID5) used in both stores \u2192 easy result merging\n\nRAG path used:  vector search via Qdrant client (top 40, exclude doc_type=drug)\ndoc_type field segments by corpus  \u00b7  payload includes content + metadata",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Single collection:  qwiva_docs\n  \u00b7 1536-dim vectors  \u00b7  Cosine distance  \u00b7  HNSW index  \u00b7  INT8 quantization\n\nFilled by:  CPG pipeline (auto)   \u00b7   PMC pipeline (auto)   \u00b7   pdf-pipeline (NOT auto)\nSame chunk id (UUID5) used in both stores \u2192 easy result merging\n\nRAG path used:  vector search via Qdrant client (top 40, exclude doc_type=drug)\ndoc_type field segments by corpus  \u00b7  payload includes content + metadata",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
