      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745900000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Three possible fixes  (pick one):\n    (a) Add a Qdrant client to pdf-pipeline/stage4_embed_insert.py  (simplest, mirrors CPG behaviour)\n    (b) Install a Supabase trigger on insert into clinical_practice_guideline_chunks  (pg_net \u2192 Qdrant REST)  \u00b7  decouples ingestion from sync\n    (c) Schedule scripts/ingest_cpg_to_qdrant.py as a Railway cron worker  (least code change, accepts a sync lag)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Three possible fixes  (pick one):\n    (a) Add a Qdrant client to pdf-pipeline/stage4_embed_insert.py  (simplest, mirrors CPG behaviour)\n    (b) Install a Supabase trigger on insert into clinical_practice_guideline_chunks  (pg_net \u2192 Qdrant REST)  \u00b7  decouples ingestion from sync\n    (c) Schedule scripts/ingest_cpg_to_qdrant.py as a Railway cron worker  (least code change, accepts a sync lag)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
